article_title: Walgreen, CVS Clinics May Increase Costs

article_metadata.description: Retail clinics may be creating new demand that adds to the rising cost of healthcare rather than reduces medical spending, according to a new analysis of the primary care option made popular by CVS Health and Walgreens. In a new study by RAND Corporation, researchers looking at a commercially insured population [...]
